NOVAK ON AMERICANS MOVING UP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In response to "House OKs Hike in Taxes on Rich" (Part A, Oct. 17): 
</P>
<P>
I have read this article carefully and perhaps I am naive but should there not 
be some mention concerning cuts in spending? We already know what legislators 
