<HEADLINE>
<P>
LET GIBSON LEAVE AND GET STRAWBERRY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
What must we faithful Dodger fans do to get Darryl Strawberry dressed in blue? 
I read he wants to come to the Dodgers and then I heard it from his own mouth 
on television. Surely the Dodger front office can come up with a solution that 
will make Strawberry, the Dodgers and the fans extremely happy in 1991. 
</P>
<P>
LYNDA M. GALLUP 
</P>
<P>
Ventura 
</P>
