<TEXT>
<P>
Santa Paula 31, Santa Clara 28 -- Linebacker Art Marcelo intercepted a Chris 
Macias pass on the Cardinal three-yard line with 25 seconds to play, preserving 
the win at Santa Paula. 
</P>
<P>
Marcelo also was on the receiving end of a four-yard scoring pass from Ben 
Fausset, their second touchdown connection, to give Santa Paula (6-2, 3-0) the 
lead for good with 2:35 to play. 
</P>
