<TEXT>
<P>
Nike -- A headline in Thursday's Times erroneously suggested that footwear 
maker Nike Inc. had canceled all television spots of a commercial parodying 
"Mister Rogers' Neighborhood." Nike will continue the campaign but no longer 
run one of the spots during prime time. 
</P>
